start both server frontend and backend in 2 separate terminals so that both are up are running

frontend: cd frontend-app then npm start
backend: cd deno then deno run --allow-net app.ts  

connect to MongoDB database:
https://deno.land/x/mongo@v0.28.0

run deno app using:
deno run --allow-net --allow-read --allow-write --allow-plugin app.ts  
deno run --allow-net --allow-read --allow-write app.ts  